<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>EcoTrack - Track Your Carbon Footprint</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/remixicon@4.2.0/fonts/remixicon.css">
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
      font-family: "Poppins", sans-serif;
    }

    body {
      background: #f4fff4;
      color: #222;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 20px 8%;
      background: white;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      z-index: 10;
    }

    header h2 {
      color: #2e7d32;
      font-weight: 700;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }

    header ul {
      list-style: none;
      display: flex;
      gap: 25px;
    }

    header ul li a {
      text-decoration: none;
      color: #333;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    header ul li a:hover {
      color: #2e7d32;
    }

    .hero {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 60px 8%;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .hero-text {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 320px;
    }

    .hero-text h1 {
      font-size: 3rem;
      color: #2e7d32;
      line-height: 1.2;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .hero-text p {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #555;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
      max-width: 500px;
    }

    .hero-text a {
      background: #2e7d32;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 25px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      font-weight: 500;
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .hero-text a:hover {
      background: #1b5e20;
    }

    .hero-img {
      flex: 1;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .hero-img img {
      width: 85%;
      max-width: 500px;
      animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
    }

    @keyframes float {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-15px); }
    }

    .features {
      padding: 80px 8%;
      background: white;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .features h2 {
      color: #2e7d32;
      font-size: 2.2rem;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
    }

    .feature-grid {
      display: flex;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 30px;
    }

    .card {
      background: #f9fff9;
      border: 1px solid #d9f9d9;
      padding: 30px 25px;
      width: 300px;
      border-radius: 15px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
      transition: 0.3s;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
    }

    .card i {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      color: #2e7d32;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }

    .card h3 {
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 25px;
      background: #2e7d32;
      color: white;
      margin-top: 60px;
    }

    footer a {
      color: #a5f3a1;
      text-decoration: none;
    }

    @media(max-width:768px){
      .hero {
        flex-direction: column-reverse;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .hero-text h1 {
        font-size: 2.4rem;
      }
      .hero-img img {
        width: 100%;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <h2>EcoTrack</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
      <li><a href="/about">About</a></li>
      <li><a href="/leaderboard">Leaderboard</a></li>
      <li><a href="/login">Login</a></li>
      <li><a href="/signUp">Sign Up</a></li>
    </ul>
  </header>

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <h1>Track. Reduce. Sustain.</h1>
      <p>EcoTrack helps you calculate and monitor your daily carbon footprint, inspiring you to make eco-friendly choices and live a greener life üåø.</p>
      <a href="/signUp">Get Started</a>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-img">
      <img src="https://media.istockphoto.com/id/1353967009/photo/sustainable-development-and-green-business-based-on-renewable-energy-reduce-co2-emission.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=-uOboxq_hAl7fFPTtYe3XSnExeeUVMVrpp0kKYNoTvI=" alt="eco illustration">
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="features">
    <h2>Why Choose EcoTrack?</h2>
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div class="card">
        <i class="ri-leaf-line"></i>
        <h3>Calculate Your Impact</h3>
        <p>Get real-time estimates of your CO‚ÇÇ emissions based on your lifestyle choices.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <i class="ri-bar-chart-line"></i>
        <h3>Visual Insights</h3>
        <p>Track your footprint with beautiful graphs and actionable analytics.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <i class="ri-community-line"></i>
        <h3>Compete & Grow</h3>
        <p>Compare your sustainability score on our global leaderboard and aim higher!</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    <p>¬© 2025 EcoTrack | Made with ‚ù§Ô∏è for a Greener Tomorrow</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
